### Adding Publications

Publications support professional citation formatting with copy-to-clipboard functionality:

```markdown
---
type: PublicationList
citationStyle: detailed   # detailed | apa | mla | chicago | ieee
groupBy: year
showCiteButton: true      # Adds "Cite" dropdown button
---

## Publications

#### journal

### Paper Title Here

First Author, Second Author, Third Author

Nature Machine Intelligence, 6(3), 234-251

2024

10.1038/s42256-024-00234

[PDF](paper.pdf)
[Code](https://github.com)
```

**Citation Styles:**
- `detailed` — Title prominent with structured metadata
- `apa` — APA 7th Edition format
- `mla` — MLA 9th Edition format
- `chicago` — Chicago Author-Date
- `ieee` — IEEE numeric style

The **Cite button** lets visitors copy citations in APA, MLA, Chicago, or BibTeX format.

### Adding Math Equations

Use the MathBlock component for LaTeX equations:

```markdown
---
type: MathBlock
showNumbers: true
background: gray
---

### Mathematical Foundations

# Core Methods

Text with inline math $E = mc^2$ and display equations:

$$\int_0^\infty e^{-x^2} dx = \frac{\sqrt{\pi}}{2}$$

### Cross-Entropy Loss

\mathcal{L}_{CE} = -\sum_{c=1}^{C} y_c \log(\hat{y}_c)

The cross-entropy loss measures divergence between distributions.
```

**Math Syntax:**
- Inline: `$...$` within paragraphs
- Display: `$$...$$` for block equations
- Named equations: H3 heading followed by LaTeX

